know that? </div><div class="t m146 xb1 h1d y355 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t m3c6 x89 h1d ye4 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Most Christians today are not blood descendants of Abraham. </div><div class="t m3c7 xb1 h1d y5d7 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Nevertheless, in what ways can we have a false hope of favor with </div><div class="t m239 xb1 h1d y5d8 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God as the chosen nation did in Christ&apos;s time? </div><div class="t m146 xb1 h1d y175 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t m2ef x89 h1d y4e5 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How can I know whether I am truly trusting in Christ or my good </div><div class="t m88 xb1 h1d y358 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">deeds for salvation? </div><div class="t m29b x2 h1c y35b ff1 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">FURTHER STUDY AND MEDITATION: </div><div class="t m3c8 xc1 h1d y5d9 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Read the chapter titled </div><div class="t m35f x2 h1d y35c ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Justified by Faith&quot; in </div><div class="t m3c9 x87 h1d y5da ff6 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Selected Messages, </div><div class="t mb0 xc2 h1d y176 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">book 1, pp. 389-398. </div><div class="t m54 x2 h1c y35e ff1 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: </div><div class="t m3ca x4f h1d y5db ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">We can be saved only by faith in Christ, never by our </div><div class="t m3ae x2 h1d y5dc ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">works, by family ties, or by church membership. Faith in Christ brings </div><div class="t m112 x2 h1d y5dd ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">both the forgiveness of sin and the power of the Holy Spirit that transforms </div><div class="t m1d5 x2 h1d y5de ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our lives. Abraham&apos;s faith in God&apos;s promises brought him the gift of right-</div><div class="t m233 x2 h1d y5df ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">eousness, and that same gift is available to every Christian who exercises </div><div class="t m17c x2 h1d y5e0 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Abraham&apos;s faith in God. Christ Himself is the Gift who comes to us by the </div><div class="t m238 x2 h1d y5e1 ff5 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Holy Spirit. </div><div class="t m3a0 x2 h1c y5e2 ff1 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">40 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
